The Polar Race
With this curvy shot I ll show you a little throwback to an awesome week in Norway, Sweden and Finland at the beginning of November. Such nice early winter in Arctic Europe / Lapland. Down to - 30°C. It's December now and at the Alps it's +20°C. Winter I miss you.

10 years old reflection.
Ten years ago I ve visited Iceland with a field course of my geography studies. Shortly after the economic crisis there was not much going on there. I could visit the country without too man photos already up in my mind cause there were not many on the internet back then. Changed a lot the last decade I would say. The focus of my photography shifted into the forests afterwards. But I still have good memories back to this trip.
